  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b9e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b83\u0baa\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The selfie that took the life of the young man",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Bandarawela, Haldumulla \u2013 Haldumulla police said that a young man tried to take a selfie near the waterfall in Sunvai Estate of Laiban Division and fell to his death.",
        "The police said that a 24-year-old youth named Madhusanga Sagara from Velimadai Kurudalava area has died.",
        "He went to the said place on Saturday (03) evening with three friends to visit the waterfall.",
        "The police said that while trying to take a selfie, he slipped and fell into the waterfall.",
        "After this, the local people and the police conducted a search operation, and the body of the youth was recovered from a ditch about 200 meters from the spot, the police added."
      ],
